<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Email</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

        <h2 style="color: #333;">Your One-Time Password (OTP)</h2>

        <p>
            Hello {{ name }},<br>
            Here is your one-time password (OTP) for authentication:
        </p>

        <div
            style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px; color: #333; border-radius: 5px;">
            {{ otpCode }}
        </div>

        <p>
            Please use this OTP to complete your authentication process. Note that this OTP is valid for a short period
            of time.
        </p>

        <p>
            If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email.
        </p>

        <p>
            Regards,<br>
            Nest-Ecommerce Team
        </p>

    </div>
</body>

</html>